parameters.name: names
parameters.description: The names of the runtime environments. Must be unique within the account. (string) ---

nested_items.name: environments
nested_items.description: Returns a list of summary details for all the runtime environments in your account.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the runtime environment was created.

nested_items.name: engineType
nested_items.description: The target platform for the runtime environment.

nested_items.name: engineVersion
nested_items.description: The version of the runtime engine.

nested_items.name: environmentArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of a particular runtime environment.

nested_items.name: environmentId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of a particular runtime environment.

nested_items.name: instanceType
nested_items.description: The instance type of the runtime environment.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the runtime environment.

nested_items.name: networkType
nested_items.description: The network type supported by the runtime environment.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the runtime environment.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A pagination token that's returned when the response doesn't contain all the runtime environments.
